"Sorry, I've never been tickalish." He looked into her eyes, and ended
up with the puppy dog face. 
"I lov..." He stoped, and just kissed her.

::DrillBit::

"Well..." He said.
"We are at the other Pred base. Phobia took command. Are teem is small,
and devided. Many, including Terrorsaur, left. Only Phobia, you, me, and
Bludgeon, are here, as far as I know. StarScream is still with us, but
he is at the Alliance base."
